# Angular features (`saovalles/src/app/features/`)

## Routing

- Register lazy routes in **`saovalles/src/app/app.routes.ts`** as children of `MainLayoutComponent` unless you intentionally need a bare layout.
- Optional nav entry: **`saovalles/src/app/core/navigation/nav.model.ts`** + **`nav.*`** keys in **`public/i18n/ca.json`** and **`es.json`**.

## i18n and SEO

- **Never** add user-visible strings for CA/ES only in templates without Transloco keys.
- For each new page: add **`meta.<page>.title`** and **`meta.<page>.description`** in **both** `ca.json` and `es.json`.
- In the component: inject **`SeoService`** and call **`bindPageToTranslations(destroyRef, 'meta.<page>.title', 'meta.<page>.description')`** once (same pattern as `informacio`, `orders`, etc.).

## Calling the order API from Angular

- Use **`OrdersApiService`** and **`environment.apiBasePath`** (`/api`). Do not hardcode `http://localhost:3000` in feature code — proxy handles dev.
